## Need Help?

1. Check logs: `railway logs --service <service-name>`
2. Check Railway status: `railway status`
3. Open dashboard: `railway open`
4. Read detailed guide: `DEPLOYMENT_GUIDE_RAILWAY.md`

Good luck with your deployment! 🚀
